{"tid":2012833,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"當全世界中央銀行再次推行量化寬鬆(QE)，Bitcoin幾個鐘前自動進入咗歷史上第三次量化緊縮(QT)","createTime":"2020-05-12T02:29:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-14T14:54:06.000Z","uid":351009,"like":12,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"075b9f2a680f75b4d57ffa72c08021b2d802143f","tid":2012833,"uid":351009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T02:29:48.000Z","msg":"Bitcoin誕生喺金融海嘯後美國出手「救市」之際<br />\n當時美國聯儲局聯同財政部幾個月內托住咗數以千億美元計嘅按揭債券，幾年之間買入超過4000億銀行業壞帳<br />\n<br />\n到今次2020經濟危機，可以肯定救市規模比上次大得多<br />\n聯儲局已經講明會無限量QE，連high yield企業債券同垃圾評級債券都會包底<br />\n財政部4-6月份單季發債3兆美元，係金融海嘯救市最高嗰季嘅6倍<br />\n而聯儲局手上嘅資產已經迫近7兆美元，高過2015年歷史高位50%<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fb5kme3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFb5kme3.png&h=39272049&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2020年唔同嘅係，上次經濟危機剛剛面世嘅Bitcoin已經累積咗11年歷史<br />\n根據Bitcoin嘅source code，每210,000個block Bitcoin嘅發行率就會減半一次(約4年出現一次)，直至6,930,000個block後唔會再有新Bitcoin出現<br />\n<br />\n就喺幾個鐘前，每block出現嘅新Bitcoin正式由12.5減半至6.25，可以話係一次量化緊縮<br />\n嚟緊4年Bitcoin將會喺現有基礎上每年增加~1.8%供應，遠低於法定貨幣嘅發行率，同時進一步接近黃金供應嘅 1.3%-1.5%<br />\n<br />\n成個減半過程自動發生，由全球Bitcoin network嘅硬件運算力維護，每一粒新幣背後都需要礦工付出能源同硬件資源，唔係某班人坐喺間房傾完撳個制就可以無限量憑空變出嚟<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OyvcWOu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOyvcWOu.png&h=be7d9393&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r6AHzAd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr6AHzAd.png&h=3fd056bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBitcoin係世上少有嘅hard and sound money<br />\n佢最大嘅價值唔係炒賣，而係opt out呢個金融體系嘅救生艇"},{"pid":"c01f6ae872e0cec3baaf47480d37490dae35ebd2","tid":2012833,"uid":144843,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T02:33:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"883570064ae6f180d5843c52457be6d672f115dc","tid":2012833,"uid":50322,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T02:34:08.000Z","msg":"如果無新發行時<br />\n<br />\n有咩人仲會維持到bitcoin 個運作"},{"pid":"b027ea6b5ce981ad796830cba3f4f632b16d6525","tid":2012833,"uid":134415,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T02:38:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">清搵人接火棒不要太明顯</span></span>"},{"pid":"4cb711370c5b3c29e7cebbfef0a5b701f11ab1ac","tid":2012833,"uid":351009,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T02:39:16.000Z","msg":"由08年開始QE就停唔到，每次遇到問題只能再次放寛<br />\n危機越大只能用更激烈嘅方法印錢，金錢某程度上已失去意義<br />\n<br />\nMoney Is Losing Its Meaning, Jared Dillian<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2020-04-15/money-has-no-meaning-anymore\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fopinion%2Farticles%2F2020-04-15%2Fmoney-has-no-meaning-anymore&d=4ZfQOx7HBA0d%2BjGm5r97HVlsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=7c871b7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2020-04-15/money-has-no-meaning-anymore</a>"},{"pid":"d6a6292d8d672ad0e68d1a2587840563d4b5ff53","tid":2012833,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b027ea6b5ce981ad796830cba3f4f632b16d6525","tid":2012833,"uid":134415,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T02:38:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">清搵人接火棒不要太明顯</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T02:45:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁快篤爆<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"8381ef7e207ba96987927f5b9d8b7c368b4b6815","tid":2012833,"uid":54884,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T02:46:23.000Z","msg":"想問下個時話量子電腦可能令呢d虛擬幣冇用係咪真呢"},{"pid":"9dc342935be52c105a162fcd5ee694e61335bf96","tid":2012833,"uid":133375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T02:47:09.000Z","msg":"但俾人hack<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b08efed39036d631f03ad3e44eead347b82b62c5","tid":2012833,"uid":351009,"like":8,"dislike":14,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"b027ea6b5ce981ad796830cba3f4f632b16d6525","tid":2012833,"uid":134415,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T02:38:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">清搵人接火棒不要太明顯</span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T02:49:00.000Z","msg":"我唔想訴諸權威，但係<br />\n<br />\nJack Dorsey (Twitter, Square 創辦人兼CEO)係咪想搵你接火棒?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C3mzqRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC3mzqRG.png&h=634fc43e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nElon Musk係咪想搵你接火棒?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pLfMgYq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpLfMgYq.png&h=b2f8c3f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPaul Tudor Jones係咪想搵你接火棒?<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=k9VpVf3g9Y0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dk9VpVf3g9Y0&d=4ZfQOx7HBA0d%2BjGm5r97HVlsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=3d85a07b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=k9VpVf3g9Y0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有Steve Wozniak, Winklevoss兄弟, Catherine Wood, Peter Thiel係咪都等緊你接貨? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定係佢哋睇到啲你睇唔到嘅嘢?"},{"pid":"7b99b92b220b98cacfb767777a3d58ba98c98fe2","tid":2012833,"uid":182185,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T02:58:55.000Z","msg":"Bitcoin唔係用黎炒 係出黎用架<br />\nBitcoin信唔過 美金都信唔過"},{"pid":"a5cae41a6b6bfd8be88fd53dcc0bf78d9ba88917","tid":2012833,"uid":351009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"883570064ae6f180d5843c52457be6d672f115dc","tid":2012833,"uid":50322,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T02:34:08.000Z","msg":"如果無新發行時<br />\n<br />\n有咩人仲會維持到bitcoin 個運作"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T03:00:20.000Z","msg":"因為Bitcoin交易要俾交易費Miner<br />\n現時Miner收入=block reward+交易費，到時理論上Miner只能賺交易費而冇晒block reward<br />\n<br />\n坦白講呢刻冇人知到時咩情況，仲有冇經濟誘因令Miner繼續工作<br />\n好多人hypothesize過但而家唔係迫切問題，因為預計喺公元2140年之後先會冇晒block reward，但過多十幾個halving cycle block reward都會趨近0"},{"pid":"336bcb6c2235952f3b41140eb2bb19407e927ae9","tid":2012833,"uid":231080,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T03:03:37.000Z","msg":"成日見到D人話搵人接貨<br />\n如果係一D 幾億市值既港股都仲可以理解<br />\n呢D國際性既人,全連登既人加埋既現金可唔可以買到0.0001% btc依家既市值..<br />\n接乜鳩貨"},{"pid":"f5d4c18f60a5530a5f359554133b4642d3415552","tid":2012833,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T03:04:26.000Z","msg":"有無安全平台"},{"pid":"fce4d834a32acae4d99ddaf5bdaaf51f5ccc8c50","tid":2012833,"uid":351009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8381ef7e207ba96987927f5b9d8b7c368b4b6815","tid":2012833,"uid":54884,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T02:46:23.000Z","msg":"想問下個時話量子電腦可能令呢d虛擬幣冇用係咪真呢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T03:06:43.000Z","msg":"已經有crypto做到quantum-resistant<br />\nBitcoin可以upgrade algorithm，不過為時尚早<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.bitcoin.it/wiki/Quantum_computing_and_Bitcoin\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.bitcoin.it%2Fwiki%2FQuantum_computing_and_Bitcoin&d=4ZfQOx7HBA0d%2BjGm5r97HVlsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=b5590394\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.bitcoin.it/wiki/Quantum_computing_and_Bitcoin</a>"},{"pid":"f7814c4427172811a3b98fd31797005f437b4f8e","tid":2012833,"uid":351009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9dc342935be52c105a162fcd5ee694e61335bf96","tid":2012833,"uid":133375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T02:47:09.000Z","msg":"但俾人hack<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T03:10:42.000Z","msg":"Bitcoin本身從未被hack，間中上新聞話被hack嘅多數係中心化交易所"},{"pid":"5e3f8a44de9220c98b502ab2e23de4d435564723","tid":2012833,"uid":