20-05-12T07:07:22.000Z","msg":"bitcoin 似黃金有限量係真，問題係人地可以一樣整 bitcoin 1, 2 , 3, 4 etc ，變相無限供應 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81b90df4f59eb01ea1ade48ed5a9db61dc1ae02a","tid":2012833,"uid":140218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T07:14:24.000Z","msg":"我幾年前有買過crypto<br />\n叫做了解過吓bitcoin背後偉大嘅諗法<br />\n<br />\n而家回頭睇返<br />\n開始覺得, 有陣時唔係idea 好就一定可以成為主流<br />\n<br />\n嘗試舉個唔好嘅例子:<br />\n好多香港人知道真普選好<br />\n但要令香港有真普選, 好難<br />\n因為在上者/掌權人/既得利益者<br />\n會用盡方法阻止呢件事發生<br />\n<br />\n(我知冇得咁比, <br />\n純粹想帶出要bitcoin 成為最通用貨幣真係好艱難嘅一步, 可能要係好多好多年後)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各位巴打請指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f028b36b5fa39118459c3dcd712af7a2e64c0cb1","tid":2012833,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T07:21:13.000Z","msg":"而家仲有冇人掘礦"},{"pid":"044d384f571463c7c961d04966cdf2d232bd841b","tid":2012833,"uid":16453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T08:37:11.000Z","msg":"過半hash rate 都黎自中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"072d3ac151802a3ae0041b510ddca6affbeb1a3a","tid":2012833,"uid":351009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"317e94434b1e825f7d4ed8dc815c264fcfdface9","tid":2012833,"uid":196712,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T03:45:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T12:29:50.000Z","msg":"香港人需要crypto exposure<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bdc9eb28c2f0242109a339bab660d6c45f58c51","tid":2012833,"uid":351009,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a7788f6461ec373d2eead6eb81a4c0f851841ad2","tid":2012833,"uid":182185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T06:20:28.000Z","msg":"其實當初要摧毀bitcoin好簡單<br />\n但點解冇人咁做？ 直到而家千億美元市值？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T13:01:18.000Z","msg":"要摧毀Bitcoin唔係咁簡單，就算一個國家ban咗都可以喺其他地方生存，中國都&quot;ban&quot;過Bitcoin好多鑊，但最多削減下佢嘅規模，唔會令佢消失<br />\n<br />\nPermissionless嘅特性代表你有硬件、電力、互聯網就可以隨時加入，即使唔合法，用peer to peer方式都可以繼續存在。除非政府大致上執行到禁令，否則一條enforceable唔到嘅法律係無意義，只會話俾人知佢對此無能為力<br />\n<br />\nBitcoin雖然有機會挑戰主權貨幣，但國家之間都有博弈，打死佢對創新科技冇好處，呢點美國國會、證監會都講得好清楚<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wFr1ooaVPjY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwFr1ooaVPjY&d=4ZfQOx7HBA0d%2BjGm5r97HVlsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=ec97c59c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wFr1ooaVPjY</a><br />\n(2分鐘開始)"},{"pid":"dd1961c5b0aa00e08548505b2836abd678e2e630","tid":2012833,"uid":351009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2da28a49f56c706075292ae7e70409816b55aed9","tid":2012833,"uid":234698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T07:07:22.000Z","msg":"bitcoin 似黃金有限量係真，問題係人地可以一樣整 bitcoin 1, 2 , 3, 4 etc ，變相無限供應 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T13:06:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/A-Map-of-Bitcoin-Forks_V2-1000x600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.visualcapitalist.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2FA-Map-of-Bitcoin-Forks_V2-1000x600.jpg&h=07a34eab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係人都可以走去fork條新chain出嚟，但冇認受性最終都會失敗"},{"pid":"3fec718886df260ba9f1fa2dc34fee4417d2b1f3","tid":2012833,"uid":351009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"81b90df4f59eb01ea1ade48ed5a9db61dc1ae02a","tid":2012833,"uid":140218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T07:14:24.000Z","msg":"我幾年前有買過crypto<br />\n叫做了解過吓bitcoin背後偉大嘅諗法<br />\n<br />\n而家回頭睇返<br />\n開始覺得, 有陣時唔係idea 好就一定可以成為主流<br />\n<br />\n嘗試舉個唔好嘅例子:<br />\n好多香港人知道真普選好<br />\n但要令香港有真普選, 好難<br />\n因為在上者/掌權人/既得利益者<br />\n會用盡方法阻止呢件事發生<br />\n<br />\n(我知冇得咁比, <br />\n純粹想帶出要bitcoin 成為最通用貨幣真係好艱難嘅一步, 可能要係好多好多年後)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各位巴打請指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T13:19:13.000Z","msg":"距離通用貨幣仲係好遙遠，亦都未必需要去到嗰步先算成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本身Bitcoin作為digital cash嘅narrative都減少咗，唔完全係一種payment方法，取而代之嘅係digital gold同crypto作為一種新資產嘅narrative<br />\n<br />\n我覺得而家最大價值係佢完全獨立於任何一個政府嘅monetary policy，係逃離呢個無中生有嘅金融體系嘅方法"},{"pid":"8364b5ee444756f68e51d80ad219a6e466336221","tid":2012833,"uid":351009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f028b36b5fa39118459c3dcd712af7a2e64c0cb1","tid":2012833,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T07:21:13.000Z","msg":"而家仲有冇人掘礦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T13:38:43.000Z","msg":"用GPU掘Bitcoin好耐之前已經賺唔到錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家基本上只有大型礦場，尤其減半後會再淘汰一批低效率嘅，美國開始有發電廠加入用極低電力成本掘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"159739efef2edcce29482ba90348d2dce50c3f89","tid":2012833,"uid":196712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T13:40:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"20f17a4e0902463362cb6160ab8ac5ed53868b70","tid":2012833,"uid":234698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"159739efef2edcce29482ba90348d2dce50c3f89","tid":2012833,"uid":196712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T13:40:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T15:26:19.000Z","msg":"用黎做炒賣工具係 perfect，廿四小時，仲可以小數點位，可惜一開左期貨市場就炒唔起...<br />\n<br />\n做貨幣唔得，因為會通縮，所以要整隻合適數碼貨幣，供應應該每年要有 2.5% 升幅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"217d3171f67c3c041fcfaa3a2b685bd7ce213a10","tid":2012833,"uid":351009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20f17a4e0902463362cb6160ab8ac5ed53868b70","tid":2012833,"uid":234698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"159739efef2edcce29482ba90348d2dce50c3f89","tid":2012833,"uid":196712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T13:40:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T15:26:19.000Z","msg":"用黎做炒賣工具係 perfect，廿四小時，仲可以小數點位，可惜一開左期貨市場就炒唔起...<br />\n<br />\n做貨幣唔得，因為會通縮，所以要整隻合適數碼貨幣，供應應該每年要有 2.5% 升幅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T15:43:11.000Z","msg":"唔多關事，CME同Bakkt交易量仲係好低，影響唔到整體市場<br />\nBitMEX 24小時交易量係佢哋20倍以上"},{"pid":"9f6ca2da69e8e235ad6644d1137b9c56b9d191ff","tid":2012833,"uid":88896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T15:48:13.000Z","msg":"如果bitcoin work，金本位銀本位都就唔會失敗"},{"pid":"dbb0049e13b8fd85f40897bec41cbf5e6e5df23b","tid":2012833,"uid":278264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f6ca2da69e8e235ad6644d1137b9c56b9d191ff","tid":2012833,"uid":88896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T15:48:13.000Z","msg":"如果bitcoin work，金本位銀本位都就唔會失敗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T15:55:51.000Z","msg":"金本位同銀本位係失敗<br />\n但係金同銀仍然係而家既硬通貨<br />\nBitcoin從開始既時候個設計已經冇可能做銀紙<br />\n等緊Bitcoin既係好似金同銀咁作為唔受政府控制既硬通貨"},{"pid":"5497e53e635b249d2836962dcf67dac064f1f5b0","tid":2012833,"uid":351009,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9f6ca2da69e8e235ad6644d1137b9c56b9d191ff","tid":2012833,"uid":88896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T15:48:13.000Z","msg":"如果bitcoin work，金本位銀本位都就唔會失敗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T16:18:53.000Z","msg":"金本位失敗係因為貨幣供應率只能等於黃金儲備增加率，但美國發行嘅金本位貨幣多過背後嘅儲備，最終只能脫勾<br />\n<br />\n但冇咗金本位等於金冇投資價值?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有金本位先至係冇投資價值，因為政府等於直接控制咗金價<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你可以睇下1976美國放棄金本位後嗰幾年金價升咗幾多倍<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/317OzO9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F317OzO9.jpg&h=0725426e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0af68eee67b189fb89728b0ad7f08c87f1f9b9c2","tid":2012833,"uid":351009,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T23:11:44.000Z","