碼貨幣既人用，唔好以為故仔先有，真實世界入邊已經發生緊"},{"pid":"929ea8dc5b3d06fa377eea122564a14b23054fd8","tid":2012833,"uid":267331,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8381ef7e207ba96987927f5b9d8b7c368b4b6815","tid":2012833,"uid":54884,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T02:46:23.000Z","msg":"想問下個時話量子電腦可能令呢d虛擬幣冇用係咪真呢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T01:17:11.000Z","msg":"係最，但你計到我條key 計唔到我個鎖，當你兩樣都計到，你咪偷<br />\n個情況係同原子彈可唔可以爆開夾萬一樣。當佢真係玩到咁，爆唔爆又有乜嘢所謂？"},{"pid":"b7e83df82313acceea724e3716bf2ac7ba6e8e8b","tid":2012833,"uid":267331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b99b92b220b98cacfb767777a3d58ba98c98fe2","tid":2012833,"uid":182185,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T02:58:55.000Z","msg":"Bitcoin唔係用黎炒 係出黎用架<br />\nBitcoin信唔過 美金都信唔過"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T01:18:04.000Z","msg":"人民幣呢？"},{"pid":"3695238427135e1a5ba4ef4bc04f0fef5f2561c4","tid":2012833,"uid":267331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5d4c18f60a5530a5f359554133b4642d3415552","tid":2012833,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T03:04:26.000Z","msg":"有無安全平台"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T01:19:12.000Z","msg":"冇野係安全，自己小心<br />\n<br />\n你身上有cash, 安唔安全？"},{"pid":"e3bb5b9bcffc37600675edabde4ce0cf6b3bd469","tid":2012833,"uid":267331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0d9b9b378d2f5cc0a590c1506d12406621a5837","tid":2012833,"uid":45518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T03:29:07.000Z","msg":"用黃金support去發行加密貨幣先至係前景"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T01:20:36.000Z","msg":"黃金嘅時代已經完咗"},{"pid":"ed5111e957abd879d279c4a7771934b110396b7e","tid":2012833,"uid":351009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8581441caa3e6a46af4c80c71c8517e72941606","tid":2012833,"uid":182185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9bdc9eb28c2f0242109a339bab660d6c45f58c51","tid":2012833,"uid":351009,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a7788f6461ec373d2eead6eb81a4c0f851841ad2","tid":2012833,"uid":182185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T06:20:28.000Z","msg":"其實當初要摧毀bitcoin好簡單<br />\n但點解冇人咁做？ 直到而家千億美元市值？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T13:01:18.000Z","msg":"要摧毀Bitcoin唔係咁簡單，就算一個國家ban咗都可以喺其他地方生存，中國都&quot;ban&quot;過Bitcoin好多鑊，但最多削減下佢嘅規模，唔會令佢消失<br />\n<br />\nPermissionless嘅特性代表你有硬件、電力、互聯網就可以隨時加入，即使唔合法，用peer to peer方式都可以繼續存在。除非政府大致上執行到禁令，否則一條enforceable唔到嘅法律係無意義，只會話俾人知佢對此無能為力<br />\n<br />\nBitcoin雖然有機會挑戰主權貨幣，但國家之間都有博弈，打死佢對創新科技冇好處，呢點美國國會、證監會都講得好清楚<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wFr1ooaVPjY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwFr1ooaVPjY&d=4ZfQOx7HBA0d%2BjGm5r97HVlsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=ec97c59c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wFr1ooaVPjY</a><br />\n(2分鐘開始)"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T01:04:29.000Z","msg":"早期掘bitcoin班cyberpunk經常持幣量都高過51% <br />\n其實係可以直接摧毁<br />\n但因為做實驗 所以佢哋派出去比其他人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T01:34:03.000Z","msg":"Proof of Work下影響安全性嘅係運算力(hash rate)，唔係持幣量<br />\n但就算hash rate超過51%都唔代表一定會受攻擊，因為理性嘅礦工冇經濟誘因攻擊自己佔主導嘅blockchain<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2014年曾經有mining pool hash rate超過咗51%，即時引起咗唔少恐慌同懷疑，因為嗰刻或多或少係靠佢作為誠實嘅參與者唔會cheat，但正常用Bitcoin本應唔駛「信」任何人嘅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後mining pool自願將hash rate降至40%以下，部份Miner(參加mining pool嘅個體)轉pool，問題解決"},{"pid":"89a005720be5ac06e78d45e92b671c4fde77e73a","tid":2012833,"uid":351009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd6ca1c592e5ba3104571d60958822b2bb9441f8","tid":2012833,"uid":267331,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b027ea6b5ce981ad796830cba3f4f632b16d6525","tid":2012833,"uid":134415,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T02:38:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">清搵人接火棒不要太明顯</span